ary alan barocas   independent director elaine crowley   independent director diane ellis   independent director earl hesterberg   independent director lisa kranc   independent director craig reasor   independent director bob aronson vice president  investor relations » insider trading biographies name description william montgoris mr william j montgoris is an independent chairman of the board of stage stores inc from august  until his retirement in june  mr montgoris served as chief operating officer of the bear stearns companies inc “bear stearns” an investment bank and securities trading and brokerage firm mr montgoris also served as chief financial officer at bear stearns from april  until october  since august  mr montgoris has served on the board of directors of carter’s inc a retailer and marketer of children’s apparel where he is a member of the audit committee from july  to november  mr montgoris served on the board of directors of officemax incorporated an office products retailer where he was a member of the audit and compensation committees michael glazer mr michael l glazer is president chief executive officer director of stage stores inc effective april  from october  to april  mr glazer served as the president and ceo of mattress giant corporation a mattress retailer from august  to october  mr glazer served as managing director of team neu a private equity firm from may  to august  mr glazer served as president and ceo of kb toys inc a toy retailer mr glazer served as a director of cpi corporation a portrait studio operator from december  to july  oded shein mr oded shein is chief financial officer executive vice president of stage stores inc from july  to january  he served in various financial positions at belk inc including vice president finance and vice president and treasurer prior to joining belk inc mr shein served as the vice president treasurer of charming shoppes inc steven hunter mr steven l hunter is executive vice president and chief information officer of stage stores inc mr hunter joined us in june  as senior vice president chief information officer and was promoted to executive vice president chief information officer in march  from may  to june  he served as senior vice president of information technology at belk inc william gentner mr william e gentner is executive vice president and chief marketing officer of the company effective june  mr gentner joined us in june  as senior vice president marketing and was promoted to executive vice president chief marketing officer in june  from june  to june  he served in various marketing positions at jc penney company inc including senior vice president strategic brands and senior vice president marketing planning and promotions russell lundy mr russell a lundy ii is executive vice president chief stores officer of stage stores inc effective january  mr lundy joined us in november  as senior vice president stores was promoted to executive vice president stores in january  and to executive vice president chief stores officer in october  prior to joining us he spent  years with peebles inc thorsten weber mr thorsten weber serves as executive vice president chief merchandising officer of the company he has been promoted to the position of executive vice president chief merchandising officer effective september   mr weber has served as our senior vice president planning and allocation since july  prior to joining us mr weber served as the senior vice president planning and allocation at kohl’s corporation from november  to july  from august  to october  mr weber held various roles of increasing responsibility in the merchandising planning and allocation areas at jcpenney company inc including most recently as senior vice president planning and allocation march  to october  and division vice president divisional merchandise manager june  to february  from july  to july  mr weber held several merchandising positions at may department stores co richard stasyszen mr richard e stasyszen is senior vice president  finance controller of stage stores inc mr stasyszen joined us in march  as assistant controller and was promoted to vice president and controller in february  in july  he was promoted to senior vice president finance and controller chadwick reynolds mr chadwick paul reynolds is senior vice president chief legal officer and secretary of stage stores inc since august  previously he spent  years with big lots inc where he most recently served as vice president deputy general counsel and assistant corporate secretary from march  to august  alan barocas mr alan j barocas is an independent director of stage stores inc he is senior executive vice president of leasing at general growth properties inc a real estate development and management firm since january  from may  to january  mr barocas was the principal of alan j barocas and associates a real estate consulting firm from june  to april  he was employed by gap inc an apparel retailer serving last as senior vice president of real estate elaine crowley ms elaine d crowley is an independent director of the company she serve as liquidation trustee for the bombay liquidation trust which oversees the liquidation of the bombay company inc “bombay” a furniture and home goods retailer since september  where she has served as senior vice president chief financial officer and treasurer since february  bombay filed for bankruptcy protection on september   from august  to september  ms crowley served as executive vice president and chief financial officer for mattress giant corporation a mattress retailer from august  to august  ms crowley served as executive vice president and chief financial officer and senior vice president controller and chief accounting officerchief financial officer for michaels stores inc an arts and crafts retailer diane ellis ms diane m ellis is as independent director of stage stores inc effective september   she is ceo of the limited a fashion retailer since august  from september  until august  ms ellis served as president and chief operating officer of brooks brothers group inc an apparel retailer earl hesterberg mr earl j hesterberg is an independent director of stage stores inc he is president ceo and a director of group  automotive inc an automotive retailer since april  from october  to april  mr hesterberg served as group vice president north america marketing sales and service for ford motor company mr hesterberg has also served as president and ceo of gulf states toyota a distributor of vehicles parts and accessories lisa kranc ms lisa r kranc is as independent director of stage stores inc effective september   she is senior vice president marketing of autozone inc an automotive aftermarket parts retailer and distributor from august  until her retirement in december  since june  ms kranc has served on the board of directors of armored autogroup inc a consumer products manufacturer craig reasor mr c clayton reasor is as independent director of stage stores inc with effect from june   he is executive vice president investor relations government affairs planning  strategy and communications of phillips  an energy manufacturing and logistics company since october  from may  to september  mr reasor served as senior vice president investor relations strategic development public affairs and public policy of phillips  from april  to april  mr reasor served as vice president investor relations and public affairs of conocophillips a crude oil and natural gas exploration and production company mr reasor is a director of phillips  partners gp llc the general partner of phillips  partners lp a publiclytraded owner developer and acquirer of crude oil refined petroleum and natural gas pipelines and terminals bob aronson basic compensation name fiscal year total william montgoris  michael glazer  oded shein  steven hunter  william gentner  russell lundy  thorsten weber  richard stasyszen  chadwick reynolds  alan barocas